      <p>
        A sketching recognition system for Finding Differences
        Game. The user will be provided two similar pictures. In one picture, some details will be
        redundant, missing or different from the other picture. User should find those differences, remove
        redundant parts, draw correct details by mouse and then click “submission”. Our sketching
